ackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 29, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104btn1719662880134.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/btn1719662880134.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/btn1719662880134.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lcp1665702754707\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /pid\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies a type library to be loaded into Uniface.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__section_w1095ab1b5b1_w1096ab1b5_w1097ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__p_d150608e1_d150609e1_d150610e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/pid</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProgId</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Prefix</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__section_w1098ab1b5b3_w1099ab1b5_w1100ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d446553e69\">\n                  \n Used With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__p_d150614e1_d150615e1_d150616e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/sti</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/mwr</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=com</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__section_w1101ab1b5b5_w1102ab1b5_w1103ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d446553e87\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__li_d52307e1_d52308e1_d52309e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__p_d150620e1_d150621e1_d150622e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProgId</var>—logical name that maps to a type library, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">word.document</code>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__li_d52310e1_d52311e1_d52312e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__p_d150623e1_d150624e1_d150625e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Prefix</var>—prefix name to precede the signature names for each type definition found in the type library.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__section_w1104ab1b5b7_w1105ab1b5_w1106ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d446553e117\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__p_d150629e1_d150630e1_d150631e1\">The switch <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/pid</span> designates that <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProgId</var> is a logical name that maps to a type library, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">word.document</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcp1665702754707__p_d150632e1_d150633e1_d150634e1\">For example, the following statement loads a type library into Uniface and converts each type definition to a Uniface signature.:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/sti /mwr=com /pid Excel.Application.8:ex</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419802\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7419802\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/pid Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /pid Specifies a type library to be loaded into Uniface. /pid ProgId { : Prefix } Used With /sti /mwr =com Parameters ProgId —logical name that maps to a type library, for example word.document Prefix —prefix name to precede the signature names for each type definition found in the type library. Description The switch /pid designates that ProgId is a logical name that maps to a type library, for example word.document For example, the following statement loads a type library into Uniface and converts each type definition to a Uniface signature.: /sti /mwr=com /pid Excel.Application.8:ex Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}